@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Researcher Adds Research

actor Researcher
participant "Frontend/UI" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
database "Database \n (Firebase)" as DB

Researcher -> UI: Open 'Add Research' page
Researcher -> UI: Fill research details and submit
UI -> API: POST /trl/case
UI -> API: POST /trl/coordinator
UI -> API: POST /trl/assessment
UI -> API: POST /trl/ip
UI -> API: POST /trl/supportment
API -> DB: Save research data
DB --> API: Success/Failure response
API --> UI: Return result (success/failure)
UI --> Researcher: Show confirmation or error

@enduml
